==English==
=== Adjective ===
'''effective'''
# Having the power to produce an [[effect]] or effects; 
# producing a decided or decisive effect; 
# efficient, serviceable, or [[operative]]; 
#*as an '''effective''' force, remedy, speech;
# actually in effect
#* The [[curfew]] is '''effective''' at midnight.

